high_descs: Cross the room to the white table with the microwave.
Pick up the pan from the table that's to the right of the microwave.
Carry the pan across the kitchen to the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf of the fridge and then remove once chilled.
Back up while holding the pan so you're lined up to the point where the counter meets the fridge.
Open the cupboard closest to the fridge and place the pan inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the counter with the microwave on it.
Pick up the fry pan behind the apple, on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room, to the round, black table, then turn left again and go to the refrigerator.
Place the fry pan in the refrigerator, on the shelf above the drawers, wait a moment for the potato to chill, than remove the fry pan from the refrigerator.
Step back from the refrigerator and move in front of the bottom cupboard next to the refrigerator.
Place the fry pan in the bottom kitchen cupboard, beside the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled, fry pan in the lower cupboard, beside the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then the left again and go to the far counter.
Pick up the plate from the right of the counter.
Carry the plate and turn around, then right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the plate inside. Take the plate out and shut the door.
Hold the plate and take a few steps backward.
Place the plate in the bottom cabinet on the right side, and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a plate and put it away in a cabinet.
